text: Hemavan or Bierke is a locality in Storuman Municipality in Västerbotten County in Sweden. In 2010, 222 people lived there. It is located on European route E12 between Storuman in Sweden and Mo i Rana in Norway. Hemavan is also known as a ski. The Hemavan Airport, is also here. == References == ==Other websites== *Hemavan & Tärnaby Category:Settlements in Vasterbotten County
